item.title: Rattus spp.
item.dc:creator: wendymoore
item.description: dead native rat. Common on the block. Live/feed in tunnels in grass root zone with long tunnels, on surface through grass, connecting sites. They do a great job of aerating the soil and also eat huge numbers of 'onion grass' bulbs. Also seen out eating cactus fruits. Confined to fence lines when stock in paddocks. 2nd shot - head close-up
